import React, { useContext } from 'react'

import { Body, Main, TextArea, N1, TextInput, Button } from './styles'
import { Text } from 'react-native'
import NumberHand from './components/NumberHand'
import { NumberHandContext, NumberHandProvider } from './contexts/NumberHandContext'

export function Adivinhe() {

    const { number1, number2, setNumber2, handleStartGame } = useContext(NumberHandContext)

    return (
        <NumberHandProvider>
            <Body>
                <Main>
                    <N1>
                        <Text>{number1} </Text>
                    </N1>

                    <TextArea>
                        <NumberHand />
                        <TextInput value={number2} onChangeText={(text) => { setNumber2(text) }} />
                    </TextArea>

                    <Button title="Verificar" onPress={handleClick} />
                </Main>

            </Body>
        </NumberHandProvider>

    )
}
